
;各種マイルストーンのチェック
;ニンゲンのミルクを出荷
@MILESTONE_CHECK_800

;母乳総出荷量が1以上で達成
SIF FLAG:母乳合計出荷量
	RETURN 1


;マイルストーン達成時の報酬
;魔術師奴隷の標的依頼（ベテラン傭兵への依頼料込み）・＜魔力枷＞入手
@MILESTONE_REWARD_800

PRINTFORML The %SAVESTR:表記／母乳% that was shipped has been well received, and they asked us to milk more and ship more.
PRINTL Eugene introduces you to 「Tera」, an acquaintance at the town hall,
PRINTL to capture a human who appears to have a lot of magical power.
PRINTL Create character.
PRINTL [ 0] OK
INPUT
CALL CHARA_MAKE_FIXED_SLAVE_SORCEROUS

;TARGETはそのまま
COST = MERCENARY_REWORD:3
CFLAG:追跡者 = 3
CFLAG:追跡人数 = 1
FLAG:傭兵バイト標的ID／ベテラン = CFLAG:ID
ITEM:魔力枷 += 1
PRINTL
PRINTL The process for capturing is: Go to [Town Hall] → Select tracking target → hire mercenaries.
PRINTL Because it's a tough job that takes a whole day, they only accept payment in advance.
PRINTL
PRINTL One mercenary was hired.
CALL PRINTL_WORD_COLOR,@"This time it was written off as an expense, but it normally costs %VALUE_DIGIT(COST)%G to hire one veteran.","黄"
CALL PRINTL_WORD_COLOR,@"Obtained 1x＜Mana Shackles＞.","水色"



;ミルク1万ml出荷
@MILESTONE_CHECK_801

SIF FLAG:母乳合計出荷量 >= 10000
	RETURN 1


;＜母乳濃厚化薬＞入手
@MILESTONE_REWARD_801

ITEM:母乳濃厚化薬 += 3
PRINTFORML The %SAVESTR:表記／母乳% that was shipped has been well received,
PRINTL and there seems to be demand for higher quality milk.
PRINTL Eugene brought a prototype quality-enhancing drug, to try out later.
CALL PRINTL_WORD_COLOR,@"Obtained 3x＜Breast Milk Enriching Drug＞.","水色"
PRINTL It can be used as a【Drug】during training。



;【濃厚母乳】の出荷
@MILESTONE_CHECK_802

;精算関数でFLAGを入れてる
SIF GETBIT(＃マイルストーン達成／濃厚母乳出荷＃)
	RETURN 1


;＜膨乳薬＞入手
@MILESTONE_REWARD_802

ITEM:膨乳薬 += 3
PRINTFORML The %SAVESTR:表記／母乳% that was shipped has been well received,
PRINTFORML and the Makai Agricultural Cooperative expressed a desire to distribute it in larger quantities.
PRINTFORML 「A lot of %SAVESTR:表記／母乳% can be squeezed from huge Breasts」,
PRINTL so Eugene created a prototype breast-expanding drug.
PRINTL You can try it later if you want to.
CALL PRINTL_WORD_COLOR,@"Obtained 3x＜Breast Expansion Drug＞.","水色"
PRINTL It can be used as a【Drug】during training。




